# WHETSTONE is a fully client-side static dApp. The frontend needs NO secrets:
# it reads and writes the live contract through the user's browser wallet.
#
# The deployer key is read only at deploy time from the repository-root .env
# (GENLAYER_PRIVATE_KEY_<n>) and is NEVER bundled into the frontend or committed.
#
# This file exists only to document that there is nothing to configure here.
